<!doctype html>
<html class="no-js" lang="zh-cn">
<head>
    <title>患者病史</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1"/>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/normalize.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/main.css">
    <script src="js/modernizr-2.8.3.min.js"></script>
    <script src="js/jquery-1.11.3.min.js"></script>
    <script src="js/config.js"></script>
    <!--<script src="js/org_main.js"></script>-->
    <script src="js/main.js"></script>
    <script src="js/plugins.js"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            background: #ffffff;
            color: #505050;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .gray_ss{
            width: 100%;
            height: 4px;
            background: #F7F7F7;
        }
        .gray_s{
            width: 100%;
            height: 10px;
            background: #F7F7F7;
        }
        .usermessage{
            width: 100%;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .userimg{
            float: left;
            width: 30%;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .userimg>img{
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            border-radius: 100%;

        }
        .othermessage{
            float: right;
            width: 40%;
            line-height: 40px;
            text-align: left;
            margin-right: 20%;
        }
        .messagetop{
            width: 100%;
            overflow: hidden;
            line-height: 39px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #CCCCCC;
        }
        .username{
            width: 50%;
            float: left;
        }
        .record{
            width: 50%;
            float: left;
        }
        .record>span{
            padding: 1px 3px;
            background: #4FC1E9;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .messagebottom{
            color: #909090;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="header" class="doctor_header">
    <div class="header-left"><p></p></div>
    <div class="header-center">患者病史</div>
    <div class="header-right"></div>
</div>

<div id="container">
    <div class="usermessage">
        <div class="userimg">
            <img src="images/doctorimg.jpg" alt=""/>
        </div>
        <div class="othermessage">
            <div class="messagetop">
                <p class="username">小明</p>
                <p class="record"><span onclick="window.location.href='org_history.html'">健康档案</span></p>
            </div>
            <div class="messagebottom">
                过往病史:肺炎、肩周炎、脑膜炎
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <p class="gray_s"></p>
</div>
<script>

</script>
</body>
</html>
